{"tid":1651783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[發夢]粉嶺手足被圍始末","createTime":"2019-10-13T12:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T07:49:06.000Z","uid":44423,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"e0037a7f005c3a0940efbbf46043e7660dae9264","tid":1651783,"uid":44423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:46:16.000Z","msg":"發夢見到 有班手足入左去爆完starfuck<br />\n就行左去爭鮮 中銀對出條路 (1號位)<br />\n有手足見到祥華邨有一部籠車出(2號位)<br />\n過左陣粉嶺火車站跑左好多防暴狗向手足方向追(~20隻 太急睇唔清楚)(3號位追去1號位)<br />\n啲手足見到之後就出馬路向4號位跑<br />\n點知馬路突然出左四部狗車<br />\n就停左係前面馬路落狗追人<br />\n四五十個手足就咁前後比人夾<br />\n又有人叫手足入爛地停車場走(P字嗰度)<br />\n但係嗰度根本係包死無得走<br />\n發現左之後就諗住跑返去1號位轉入商場<br />\n但係2 3號位啲狗已經到左1號位<br />\n大量手足就係嗰度同狗撞 <br />\n最後廿幾個手足就咁比狗拉左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Egk13F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Egk13F.jpg&h=f648d3e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c8a18eb0cdd8352ba98a91e6452bfbb137134ee","tid":1651783,"uid":44423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:47:04.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"2e03ccd5dd8f343e1d6fc7c00c2778dd5a15ce9a","tid":1651783,"uid":44423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:47:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"96fcd38a26bf483093fc8feb3ea534869a1bf506","tid":1651783,"uid":44423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:47:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be945824b14d6bc078c7ba08f401b1940c800cbc","tid":1651783,"uid":44423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:47:35.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"d638b9931dfede56a3fc871d4a2d95c52217cce1","tid":1651783,"uid":44423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:47:49.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"0f250a9204a10d3bf4a258d658ac413df331a6bb","tid":1651783,"uid":44423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:48:08.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"cc527c9c46f69802ef80edf388bfcc1ac7e54cb9","tid":1651783,"uid":44423,"like":